fields.description:
Crossfit? We're thinking MOSHFIT! The OverMuch® training wear line is here to keep you dry in the pit.

  • Training top
  • Smooth and flexible materials
  • Keeps you cool when active
  • Transports moisture away instead of absorbing it
  • Features the Metallica logo on front and the OverMuch® logo on the back of the neck


OverMuch® TechWeave™ is made from 90% polyester and 10% Spandex to make it quick drying, ultra soft , durable and comfortable. Wash in 30 degrees, do not use fabric softener.

fields.name: Renegade VIP Experience (EURO TOUR 2022)
fields.description:
Hear soundcheck and chat with Renegade!

Renegade VIP Experience Package includes:

  • Soundcheck Access
  • Band Q&A
  • Exclusive VIP Laminate
  • Limited Edition Pre-signed Poster
  • One Group Photo with All Guests + Renegade (Emailed at a later date)
  • Hassel-free Merch Shopping
  • First in Line at Door
  • Tickets to the show are NOT included in this package. Please make sure you have purchased tickets and have your ticket in hand upon entering event.


A representative will contact you within one week of selected show date with complete details on meet time and location. Know that most meet and greets begin by checking in with valid ID and your order confirmation at the venues will call or box office early afternoon.
